{"tid":1544050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大學生會署理會長胡國泓校園內遇襲 疑遭內地生揮拳打傷臉","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T14:26:05.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"75fcc1d9c5e744e2d5260f83dd5a477fd0a507ad","tid":1544050,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190905/large/1567684630_6372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190905%2Flarge%2F1567684630_6372.jpg&h=1680899a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190905/large/1567684630_929e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190905%2Flarge%2F1567684630_929e.jpg&h=fd9b372f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡國泓傷勢。理大學生會提供(讀者提供圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190905/large/1567684630_a4a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190905%2Flarge%2F1567684630_a4a4.jpg&h=62fe6b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑打人者。互聯網圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n理大學生會署理會長胡國泓於校園內遇襲！晚上7時許，警方接獲報案指胡國泓遭人打傷，消息指胡事發時於理大民主牆對開為校園活動維持秩序，其間遭一名疑似內地學生揮拳打傷右邊臉，在場學生見狀立即喝止。理大學生會其後在Telegram頻道公佈事件，校董李傲然亦確認事件，學生會已就署理會長遇襲一事報警。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190905/60013932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60013932&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=6a11a4b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60013932&h=bc4c1c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190905/60013932</a>"},{"pid":"c69c95a71a1c706d35629d3d35944970324d08d4","tid":1544050,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbf3e3e5d696b64796a6b43ffe1c65f4769e35b4","tid":1544050,"uid":258034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"私左佢啦<br />\n叫人咪拍片"},{"pid":"efbebd9107a7653c99dbb34ee064cf20cbd2bd34","tid":1544050,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbf3e3e5d696b64796a6b43ffe1c65f4769e35b4","tid":1544050,"uid":258034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"私左佢啦<br />\n叫人咪拍片"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"咪係, 最好有個支那生重傷<br />\n嚇到佢地退學最好"},{"pid":"0d5d09f5ebb6a773127f560fdedba1cf12769658","tid":1544050,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da3e46ee14cdaee22a1c774fa5fe76cb4443fa78","tid":1544050,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d5d09f5ebb6a773127f560fdedba1cf12769658","tid":1544050,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efbebd9107a7653c99dbb34ee064cf20cbd2bd34","tid":1544050,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbf3e3e5d696b64796a6b43ffe1c65f4769